PrecisAppointment of CAMILLE BELLIVEAU, of Shediac, New Brunswick, selected from a list of nominees submitted by the Province of New Brunswick, as a director of the Board of Management of the Canada Customs and Revenue Agency, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective November 1, 1999.
